Package repository

Class PatientRepository

java.lang.Object
repository.PatientRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPatientRepository, IRepository<model.users.Patient>
public class PatientRepository extends Object implements IPatientRepository
An implementation of IPatientRepository that operates on Patient data models. It extends the functionality of a UserRepository through dependency injection to focus on Users that are specifically Patients.
Since:
2024-10-29
